CLARIFICATION OF INTENT

This license applies to the text, structure, and presentation of the
CORE AI Safety Charter and associated documents in this repository.

It does NOT prohibit:
- Referencing this Charter in commercial or non-commercial systems
- Implementing policies, tests, or architectures inspired by this work
- Building proprietary tools or safety layers that cite this Charter

It DOES prohibit:
- Selling this Charter or its documents as a product
- Republishing this work as a paid or gated offering
- Claiming exclusive ownership of the Charter itself

The intent of this license is to preserve this work as a public reference
and safety foundation, while allowing broad adoption and implementation.

